{"tid":1994619,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍拘3人涉以威嚇手段脅迫廣告商停止向無線電視及東方日報刊登廣告","createTime":"2020-04-29T15:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T08:41:35.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d281845243df229a814de2adfd4aafd2d1513286","tid":1994619,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"警拘3人涉網上發表針對兩間傳媒機構恐嚇言論<br />\n29.04.2020 22:40<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕兩男一女，涉嫌與近日有人在網上發表針對兩間傳媒機構的恐嚇言論，煽惑他人傷害該機構記者及破壞攝影器材，和在未經授權下取用廣告商的商業資料，以威嚇手段脅迫廣告商停止刊登廣告有關。消息指，兩間機構分別是無線電視及東方日報。被捕人士介乎21至37歲、分別以「串謀刑事恐嚇」及「煽惑他人進行刑事毀壞」等被捕，不排除更多人被捕。警方亦檢獲多部手提電話及電腦，相信與案有關。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，有關行為嚴重影響商業活動自由進行及妨礙新聞自由，譴責所有形式恐嚇行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284255&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1284255%26csid%3D261_341&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjwwvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=a41c9e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284255&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"e2715ce2e2459c3cb6c38275dbc18596c197b284","tid":1994619,"uid":66507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c70d1dd8703cc03d93a114d45d59ec891da150f","tid":1994619,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"哇 上網話唔買你D野都唔得<br />\n咁全世界快D去TVB落廣告啦 賺硬架"},{"pid":"fdc5c91bd5ad89b620565a5076a318e45d77db05","tid":1994619,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"選擇性執法<br />\n垃圾黑警死全家"},{"pid":"b89a2132e235d14b5e297d35511acad91441c588","tid":1994619,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/o